  "title": "QAQC Engineer",
  "description": "<p>The QAQC Engineer’s primary responsibility is to ensure the maintenance, implementation, and compliance of the established Integrated Management Systems (IMS) of the company. The QAQC Engineer assists the Snr. QAQC Manager in ensuring that services provided by the company meet established standards of quality. Other duties of the QAQC Engineer include quality evaluation and control of construction work on project sites and identifying and correcting improper quality control  practices.</p>",
